org.researchstack.backbone.storage.file

Class UnencryptedProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.researchstack.backbone.storage.file.UnencryptedProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EncryptionProvider

    public class UnencryptedProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements EncryptionProvider
    Use this class as the EncryptionProvider when you want to store all data without encryption. Pin protection is still available, but will not be used to encrypt files written.
